Why Join MISA?

To hear from people currently working in the 'real world'
Ask questions and get answers about IT/IS careers
Learn about the newest technologies and trends being used in the IT/IS field today
Learn about companies before sending them your resume
Gain exposure to as much information as possible before you graduate!
Get a leg up on a highly competitive job market
What Happens at MISA Meetings?

Representatives from area businesses, recent IT retirees and local technology experts present at our meetings. Most visiting companies have internships and full-time positions available. Meetings are casual, but if interested in a company, members are encouraged to bring resumes and "dress to impress." Pizza and pop are provided to all members during meetings.
Benefits of Membership:

Scholarships
Internships
Resume Building
Learn about life after graduation
